getUnmodifiableSpatialElements

public final java.util.List<SpatialElementIfc> getUnmodifiableSpatialElements()
Returns an unmodifiable view of the spatial elements in this cell The list is unmodfiable, i.e. you can't change the list, but you can still change the elements in the list. WARNING: Don't change the elements unless you really know what you are doing.
